Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:04.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ax!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have talked to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've noticed it and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.07,0:02:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...I defended myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How persistent...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Since your rank of authority is higher than us,\Nwhile you're conscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't control the Seraphim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...Dawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucci!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna save this girl,\Nwe gotta go see Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fooling around! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm spinning too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Get inside the factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Seraphim are unstoppable! There's nothing\Nto be gained by fighting amongst ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still children. I'm afraid to imagine\Nwhat they'll be like when they grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sentomaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That power is what's the matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The power that the brat Jimbei is using!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the Swim-Swim Fruit power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Swim-Swim Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my sworn brother\Nfrom the Donquixote Family...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...Senor Pink's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There can't be two of the same Fruit\Nin this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean he died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You've noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He is currently being held in Impel Down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee! Don't make me worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...you duplicated the Devil Fruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The Devil Fruits...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...can be made artificially,\Nbut only the Zoan type!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Caesar's Smiles are ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he can go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Smiles are too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one out of ten people at most\Nwill gain power by eating one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones who didn't receive power\Nwill be forced to smile all the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hearing that name\Nmakes me wanna puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, putting that aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably even the special types of Fruits\Ncan all be replicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...given tons of money and time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm not sure if they'll awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I did all I could to replicate the Logia types,\Nbut it's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...for the Paramythia types, I found\Nif I can get its user's Bloodline Elements,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can create a special blood infusion\Nand by administering it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can let someone have its power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...the blood flowing through their arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Green Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you create blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Love-Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...Mellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Seraphim are the peak of what our science\Ncan achieve as far as I can deduce!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ursa Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be said that they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...the strongest form of humanity\Nin the history of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The strongest form of humanity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why the Seven Warlords\Nwere abolished?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you create something that's\Nstronger than the Seven Warlords! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're essentially the Navy's weapons...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They are a threat to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sentomaru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Sentomaru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did your silly friend go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.00,0:11:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's not my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...Dawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How powerful is he?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...passing out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you taking so much time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Vacuum Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a kind Hancock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been a big help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just following orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We will be departing in one minute.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please refrain from\Nrushing onto the rocket.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ax!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you with Old Man Punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're going the opposite direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The doors will close soon.\NPlease be careful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get him off the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please refrain from rushing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For your safety,\Nplease fasten your seat belt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All engines running.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are departing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been on such...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?! Where's Vegapunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Luffy! A lot has happened!\NI'll tell you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm getting used to it?\NNo, it's too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, ship doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.58,0:18:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna be like that?!\NStraw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Departing Fabriophase, bound for Labophase.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Transit duration...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...is 32 seconds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,--{\i1}We have arrived.{\i0}\N--How fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All subsequent rockets are cancelled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Labophase, Egghead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Frontier Dome, fortified.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have intruders. It is dangerous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Researchers, please evacuate to the factory\Nand seal the building.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get him off the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dive into the Sea of Information!\NThe Punk Records Library!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Lilith, one of the Satellites of\NDr. Vegapunk, the genius scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:21:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Edison, also Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll introduce this one! Senor Pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He is an officer of the Donquixote Family\Nand a Swim-Swim Fruit power user.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He can swim through the ground and walls,\Nanywhere except the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks ridiculous\Nbut his behavior is so hard-boiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.04,0:22:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born on June 12th,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and likes his wife Russian's homemade dishes\Nand a cocktail called gimlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.47,0:22:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So hard-boiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop climbing all over me, you little tramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.97,0:22:38.64,On Top,,0,0,0,,SENOR PINK - AN OFFICER\NDONQUIXOTE FAMILY (DIAMANTE ARMY)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.64,0:22:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go hang out with younger guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's quite a guy who would defend his friends\Nand even random cats with his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither he nor Franky gave an inch\Nin their one-on-one battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Franky won in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but he called Senor Pink "brother"\Nand praised him for his expert fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.62,0:22:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Very intense!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:23:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, this guy has a hidden past,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.08,0:23:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's uncool to mention it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see his hard-boiled behavior\Nin person someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.21,0:23:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.17,0:23:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen it,\Ndonate to our research fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Frontier Dome\Nhas been fortified 100 percent!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}CP-0 is plotting to capture the Labophase{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}while Vegapunk is looking to escape\Nfrom the Future Island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.90,0:23:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While each of them\Npursues their own agenda,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.16,0:23:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}an accident occurs\Nthat changes the fate of the island!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sinister Schemes!\NThe Operation to Escape Egghead"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.75,0:23:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
